
'''''Mapantsula''''' ni filime  yo muri [[Afurika]] yepfo yo mu 1988 iyobowe na Oliver Schmitz kandi yanditswe na Schmitz na Thomas Mogotlane<ref>Mapantsula and the Culture of Resistance in South Africa - jstor <nowiki>https://www.jstor.org</nowiki> › stable</ref> . Ivuga amateka ya Johannes 'Panic' Themba Mzolo (Mogotlane), umujura wigihe gito, yashyizwe inyuma ya Apartheid<ref>Mapantsula | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › mapantsula</ref> . Iyi filime yakoresheje ibintu byagaragaye hagati y’igihe cya Panic yatewe n’umugororwa we w’ivangura rya 'Stander' (Marcel Van Heerden) hamwe n’ibibera mu mujyi wa Johannesburg mu mujyi wa Soweto byerekana akarengane abirabura bo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo bahuye nako mu gihe cya apartheid ndetse n’urugamba rwabo rwo gutora<ref>Mapantsula - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › mapantsula</ref><ref>New South African cinema: Mapantsula and Sarafina <nowiki>https://academic.oup.com</nowiki> › screen › article-pdf</ref>. Iyi filime ikoresha cyane imyigaragambyo ya politiki, ubugome bwa polisi, n’itandukaniro rishingiye ku moko kugira ngo tugaragaze ingaruka za apartheid ku Birabura bo muri [[Afurika]] yepfo<ref>Mapantsula - Film at Lincoln Center <nowiki>https://www.filmlinc.org</nowiki> › films › mapantsula</ref>. Yerekanwe mu gice cya Un Certain Regard mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 1988<ref>Mapantsula - Film at Lincoln Center <nowiki>https://www.filmlinc.org</nowiki> › films › mapantsula</ref> .  Iyi filime yatoranijwe nk'iyinjira muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo muri Filime nziza y'indimi z'amahanga mu bihembo bya 62 bya Osama, ariko ntiyemerwa nk'umukandida. <ref>Margaret Herrick Library, Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences</ref>

== UMUTWE ==
